Yes, he is my boyfriend.

16
00:01:27,360 --> 00:01:29,800
I'm not old-fashioned or anything,

17
00:01:32,120 --> 00:01:33,200
but why didn't you tell me

18
00:01:34,080 --> 00:01:35,920
